<p><strong>附录 CN-001-B：建筑</strong></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;点击此处代表你坚持进行访问。输入鉴定密码：The&nbsp;spider&nbsp;weaves&nbsp;the&nbsp;curtains&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;palace&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Caesars</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;收合</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div class="scp-image-block block-center" style="width:100%;"><img src="http://scpsandboxcn.wdfiles.com/local--files/collab:rigil-kentaurus-001-ii/scr00035.png" style="width:100%;" alt="scr00035.png" class="image" />
